Hi Marcs,

These are the formulas you need to convert from Yxy to radiance-rgb:

X=x*Y/y;
Z=(1-x-y)*Y/y;
r=  2.565*X -1.167*Y -0.398*Z;
g= -1.022*X +1.978*Y +0.044*Z;
b=  0.075*X -0.252*Y +1.177*Z;

Raphael

